  "description": [
    "4 IMMIGRANTS OFFER BIG PROBLEM TO U S Officials Find Many Vexatious Cases to Deal With in Protecting Americas Interests Continued From First Page it for she has already been here too long I know what lam talking about because she is my sisterinlaw and she has done nothing but make trouble between me and my man ever since she came over here and I want that you should aend her back on the first boat because the longer she stays the worse It will be for this great land of j America Sonia did go backnot because she Was a domesetic troublemaker how ever but because her visitors visa had expired Frog Brings Deportation All kinds of conflicts of human na ture result in deportations One of the most curious that I recall involved a frog The facts related to me by the Immigration agents who investigated j the case began in the bathtub of the servants quarters of a large Pennsyl j vania estate On a certain hot Sum mers day Katrina H recently ar j rived from Germany sought relief by immersing herself in a tub of cold water She had hardly become com j fortably established"
